Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我慢慢地告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你不知不覺間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這社會發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:07 SOCIETY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是看著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為網絡上的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐近來怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(警告)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網上世界和現實世界根本就是連接的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管肉體在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意識都不被限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總經理你還在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是晚餐時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三分鐘後樓下等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不現實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有哪裡奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你又和以前一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓你高興 我們才帶你到處去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想讓你開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真的是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 如果你不喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！ 沒這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 要你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友嘛 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡情報中心的防火牆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人入侵破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在網絡的情況完全混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在播導的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是現在播導的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是各位收到時可能是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者已經是昨天的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS在網絡世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為有著巨大影響力 武裝騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組員身份不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不單只操作情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也研發非法的機器 連金融也可以自由操作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 沒有相關資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近也沒有見到玲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音是個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象徵性 意志 力量 眼神 存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是KNIGHTS的成員嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是宅即便 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要印章是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 印章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我做這樣兼職的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全買不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要更加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我要更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不明白的地方可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會盡力幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以教我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 對這個我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都像這樣勾引閒來無事的家庭主婦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒啦 怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 待會我可以去欣也家玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩遊戲的話透過網絡不就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他要教我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡和現實是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩倉玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能請你和我們走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並不是勉強你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是請求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並沒有傷害你肉體的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？ 我不想再留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎 連這樣我都做得到 看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以在網絡和現實世界來去自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很有資格加入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我加入KNIGHTS吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讚賞我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我一個人獨自發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往後你們便有專用的機密網絡線路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我成為KNIGHTS的一員吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用了很多方法來入侵防火牆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連程序也重新修改了 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這舊機型完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一直都是用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經沒有心力去學習新型電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經都這把年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我像你一樣年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡的Jumper設定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將這…還有這…拉下來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 你能幫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自動登錄完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你也是KNIGHTS的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那小孩電腦網的遊戲都算相當出色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有一個構想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請你讓我加入KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡上是沒有現實世界的政治性 國界線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無政府主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一些壞事的可憐蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那種遭遇太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS似乎完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你到底自覺多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在網絡上的存在是極端不自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後為什麼KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這樣的你 特別的感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在…說…什…麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定你曾經跟這個集團有過直接的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS就是要利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎樣都一定要阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然會保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道你們正在進行 當然我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…那件事是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網上真的有神存在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我相信加入你們後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以理解 因為到時我就有和你們相同的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了 終於來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了真正的名字也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他們都是沒有名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩倉玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和網絡上的玲音是同一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母是你真正的父母？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你姐姐是你真正的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在說什麼？ 當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸的生日是哪一天？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽的生日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是何時結婚的？ 自由戀愛？ 相親？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的生日…結婚…他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們從來沒提過？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有和他們一起慶祝生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小時候是怎樣生活的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的一點都不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的一點都不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很嘮叨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是問些無關重要的問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你是網上的玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全裝置消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡和現實中的界線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經漸漸的崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們認為這樣很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認為很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如她所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會發生一件很有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要靜靜看便足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你工作做完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了 媽媽也很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了！
